('12e46331-cb1c-5410-9b03-d105b80a66d4', '0b84cf73-39ca-4b1e-baf6-2b14823487ff', 'We had a lot of fun ___ the summer vacation.', '我們在暑假期間玩得很開心。', 'during', 'since', 'until', 'with', 'dur 表示持續', 'dur 代表持續 → 在...期間', '2026-07-05 07:10:32', '2026-07-05 07:10:32'),
('68aac975-0f62-5919-a603-0ecab58e5954', '5bec63cc-b183-4afc-8b3b-bb5928b178b1', 'Please complete this English ___ before you go home.', '請在回家前完成這項英文習題。', 'exercise', 'song', 'story', 'game', 'ex (向外) + erc (做) → 運用知識', 'ex (向外) + erc (做) → 把學過的知識拿出來做 → 習題', '2026-07-07 05:13:32', '2026-07-07 05:13:32'),
('61a6ba28-7867-5c55-b6c1-fb643670a1f8', '82e6ce3b-8491-48d6-bbf1-f411056d94ce', 'The teacher will ___ the new grammar rules to the students.', '老師會向學生解釋新的文法規則。', 'explain', 'borrow', 'forget', 'enjoy', 'ex- (向外) + plain (平坦/清楚) → 使事情變得平坦清楚 → 解釋。', 'ex (向外) + plain (平坦) → 把事情講得平平整整、清清楚楚 → 解釋。', '2026-07-07 05:25:28', '2026-07-07 05:25:28'),
('babccd53-3755-5827-8dde-3d24f0073d58', 'b214ca2d-6ffe-4cbb-a8b3-24f11be7c5e9', 'The old man is very happy because his ___ is coming to visit him today.', '這位老人很高興，因為他的孫子今天要來看他。', 'grandson', 'doctor', 'neighbor', 'driver', 'grand (大的/祖輩的) + son (兒子)', 'grand (大的) + son (兒子) → 隔代的人，即孫子。', '2026-07-07 13:58:18', '2026-07-07 13:58:18'),
('aac563d5-c8c3-5422-a6c4-98b4041bef90', '0eff5bef-ec8e-4d33-ae9f-0cec88b84610', 'After summer vacation, Tim went to the barber to get a ___.', '暑假過後，Tim 去了理髮店剪頭髮。', 'haircut', 'sandwich', 'bicycle', 'textbook', 'hair (頭髮) + cut (剪) → haircut (理髮)', '想像 hair (頭髮) 被 cut (剪) 掉，就是 haircut (理髮)！', '2026-07-07 14:11:45', '2026-07-07 14:11:45'),
('a6472dcb-7931-56cd-beb3-201c902e8098', '9e6f9c2c-47a8-44a5-9753-8fc345a74337', 'My grandfather is 80 years old, but he is still very ___.', '我祖父80歲了，但他仍然非常健康。', 'healthy', 'sleepy', 'angry', 'lucky', 'health (名詞：健康) + y (形容詞字尾) → 健康的', '想要保持 health (健康) 就要多運動，變成 healthy (健康的)。', '2026-07-07 14:58:38', '2026-07-07 14:58:38'),
('0864ed52-6d57-5fb0-a6e0-e596b5b8c5b4', '9ecc438d-7cbb-4420-94f7-b070be628538', 'Don''t forget to bring your ___ to school.', '別忘了把你的家庭作業帶到學校。', 'homework', 'lunch', 'money', 'water', '由 home (家) 與 work (工作) 組成的複合名詞。', 'home (家) + work (工作) → 在家做的功課。', '2026-07-08 07:53:10', '2026-07-08 07:53:10'),
('7e1f2781-38f6-516a-b727-953299a7305c', '788361a5-b978-4645-8225-b107907e2c5f', 'He is ___ of his brother''s new toy.', '他很嫉妒他哥哥的新玩具。', 'jealous', 'scared', 'proud', 'tired', 'jealous 為形容詞，表示「嫉妒的」。', '看到別人有自己想要的東西時，心裡那種酸酸的感覺 → jealous。', '2026-07-08 10:07:41', '2026-07-08 10:07:41');
